Dialogue: 1,0:00:12.73,0:00:15.13,Line CN,,0,0,0,,不要问我 — 我什么都没看见
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.13,0:00:18.73,Line CN,,0,0,0,,井出突然就发神经 然后做了不知道什么事{不是很确定。思路是：这里go off采用类似bomb/alrm go off的引申，指代之前井出焦急和搜索沙滩，也是第三话里森看见的最后一件常识范畴内的事。}
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.17,0:00:27.67,Line CN,,0,0,0,,她从沙滩回来的时候 我可担心了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.67,0:00:29.68,Line CN,,0,0,0,,因为她很久都昏迷不醒
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.70,0:00:32.71,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但是她醒来后 突然变得活泼开朗
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.71,0:00:34.88,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这一定是因为她感受到我对她的爱了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.88,0:00:38.10,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这是头一次 我觉得自己像是她的母亲了
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.10,0:00:40.02,Line CN,,0,0,0,,直升机 直升机！
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.22,0:00:42.32,Line CN,,0,0,0,,世界要颠倒了！
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.32,0:00:44.86,Line CN,,0,0,0,,气死我了！受不了！
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.86,0:00:47.19,Line CN,,0,0,0,,都怪那个混蛋耳机！
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.19,0:00:50.73,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这是 Medical Mechanica 采取的紧急措施
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.76,0:00:53.28,Line CN,,0,0,0,,人格的改变应该是其副作用
Dialogue: 1,0:00:53.63,0:00:54.95,Line CN,,0,0,0,,哦！熨斗！
Dialogue: 1,0:00:54.97,0:00:57.77,Line CN,,0,0,0,,也被称为熨平世界的机器{求助}
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.44,0:01:01.04,Line CN,,0,0,0,,实话说 我确实觉得她挺可爱的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.38,0:01:07.91,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那个女孩…
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.95,0:01:09.32,Line CN,,0,0,0,,她不是云雀弄
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.06,0:01:13.29,Line CN,,0,0,0,,晨安！同窗们！{top of the morning好像是个爱尔兰起源的有点古老的早晨问候…我想不出啥古典的说法了}{就这样吧}
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.29,0:01:15.89,Line CN,,0,0,0,,酷美来了！亮闪闪 早早的
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.56,0:01:18.56,Line CN,,0,0,0,,她好可爱
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.11,0:01:40.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,晴子老师 求求你 做点什么吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.25,0:01:43.88,Line CN,,0,0,0,,都是你的错 你没有像我说的那样摘下耳机
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.88,0:01:45.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉！
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.92,0:01:48.49,Line CN,,0,0,0,,时间宝贵 你却在耽误时间
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.82,0:01:51.12,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你知道你需要做什么 所以赶快行动
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.56,0:01:54.79,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-你喜欢这样打扮成女仆吗？-Medical Mechanica
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.03,0:01:57.60,Line CN,,0,0,0,,在那里才能移除耳机
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.86,0:02:00.93,Line CN,,0,0,0,,然后我们才能去追寻他
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.30,0:02:04.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我们没有别的选项
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.07,0:02:10.38,Line CN,,0,0,0,,希望不要迟到！
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.31,0:02:16.78,Line CN,,0,0,0,,啊 痛
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.25,0:02:19.25,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.27,0:02:21.02,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.05,0:02:22.55,Line CN,,0,0,0,,画好了！
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.29,0:02:29.35,Line CN,,0,0,0,,用一个字来说 这是一首歌！
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.35,0:02:32.16,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-一首歌？-对的！
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.16,0:02:35.50,Line CN,,0,0,0,,宇宙里没有氧气 所以谁也听不见你唱歌！
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.50,0:02:40.71,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但是星星转啊转啊转 它们齐声歌唱！
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.91,0:02:48.01,Line CN,,0,0,0,,星星的音乐？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.01,0:02:49.82,Line CN,,0,0,0,,啊！我的工作！
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.46,0:02:58.76,Line CN,,0,0,0,,啊 好棒！他们要安装一个新的设施！
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.76,0:02:59.96,Line CN,,0,0,0,,赞！
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.50,Line CN,,0,0,0,,时间到了 付钱吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.37,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.31,0:03:16.11,Line CN,,0,0,0,,合作愉快 拿着
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.44,0:03:19.51,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-我买了这个吗？-正是如此 那么
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.11,Line CN,,0,0,0,,下次服务见
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.22,0:03:28.05,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-那是啥？-就是个海盗船呗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.05,0:03:30.19,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好逊 我们回家吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.86,0:03:31.88,Line CN,,0,0,0,,对不起 我迟到了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.88,0:03:34.73,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你来了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:34.79,0:03:36.55,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那是什么 屯吉先生？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.56,0:03:38.22,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这个吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.22,0:03:41.23,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这是我们新的游乐项目
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.17,0:03:44.82,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你找不到它了？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.82,0:03:47.37,Line CN,,0,0,0,,别像个小孩一样 赶快去找
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.41,0:03:51.36,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我已经到处都找过了 就是找不到！
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.36,0:03:55.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那么大的一个花盆 你居然也能搞丢了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.10,0:03:56.82,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你就不能重新做一个吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.84,0:04:00.05,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这是用这家伙的部件造出来的独一无二之物
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.07,0:04:04.36,Line CN,,0,0,0,,以我们的科技 不可能从零开始制作出来的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.94,0:04:10.23,Line CN,,0,0,0,,对了 你有没有看到这里放着的那个熊雕？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.23,0:04:14.12,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你真是…算了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.13,0:04:15.80,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我回来了 伙计们
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.16,0:04:18.87,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我们要用它来监视… -是的我知道
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.89,0:04:21.57,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我们要逆转 N.O. 的流动
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.59,0:04:25.88,Line CN,,0,0,0,,如果我们假设 N.O. 是可以吸引物体的力量 那么…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.88,0:04:30.68,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我明白 那么我们应该能够逆转它的方向
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.58,Line CN,,0,0,0,,没错 然后
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.29,0:04:45.63,Line CN,,0,0,0,,1，2 出拳！现在 逆转顺序！
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你们在干什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.70,0:04:51.47,Line CN,,0,0,0,,嘿 爱子 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.49,0:04:54.97,Line CN,,0,0,0,,哦 看啊 你很有潜力！
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.99,0:04:58.44,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这拳头真不错！啊！
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.46,0:05:01.21,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你又让这个到处物色冠军的家伙到我们家里来了？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.21,0:05:02.05,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你觉得如何？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.08,0:05:04.58,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我们俩可以站在世界巅峰—
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.62,0:05:09.44,Line CN,,0,0,0,,她的拳头像流星一样！
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.29,0:05:15.43,Line CN,,0,0,0,,邻居们都在议论为什么有一个怪异的流浪汉经常到我们家来
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.32,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 -你爸没有做错什么
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.32,0:05:20.90,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你爸是一个冠军
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.92,0:05:23.20,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你原谅我们的话 我就给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:22.70,TopLeft,,0,0,0,,大豆游乐园\N入场券
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.77,0:05:27.21,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你老是用这些免费门票来道歉
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.04,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这些票到底是从哪里来的？
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.04,0:05:31.11,Line CN,,0,0,0,,呃那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.97,Line CN,,0,0,0,,关于这个…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.97,0:05:36.15,Line CN,,0,0,0,,比起这个 我更想要 SPA 或者度假地的通票
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.17,0:05:38.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我知道游乐园增添了新的设施
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.12,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但不过是个无聊的海盗船罢了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.36,Line CN,,0,0,0,,真的装了?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.38,0:05:47.58,Line CN,,0,0,0,,确定是海盗船吗？！-对啊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.25,0:05:50.33,Line CN,,0,0,0,,他们做到了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.46,Line CN,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.67,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这对我们将是个大问题
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.70,0:05:57.36,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你们在讲些什么呢 -喂 爱子
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.36,0:05:59.67,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你知道那个熊雕到哪里去了吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.97,0:06:06.11,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你能来做测试运行的小白鼠 我真是很感激
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.11,0:06:08.18,Line CN,,0,0,0,,没关系 这是工作的内容
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.20,0:06:11.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,真是个好小伙子
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.12,0:06:13.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,以及 做这个是有额外奖金的对吧？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.34,Line CN,,0,0,0,,没错 你需要钱吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.36,0:06:17.99,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.61,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我想要买一个礼物
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.63,0:06:23.80,Line CN,,0,0,0,,梦 是梦！
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.83,0:06:26.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我们为什么要做梦？！
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.23,Line CN,,0,0,0,,难道只是因为它被称作为梦？{求助}
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.25,0:06:30.60,Line CN,,0,0,0,,有睡觉时做的梦 也有醒着的时候做的梦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.50,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我们睡觉或者醒着都会做梦
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.50,0:06:34.64,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我梦到一个梦！我梦见自己从梦里醒来！
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.64,0:06:35.51,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.14,Line CN,,0,0,0,,看这里
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.65,Line CN,,0,0,0,,耳机是没有办法移除的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.65,0:06:44.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,它们钻入酷美的头部已经太深了
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.12,0:06:46.22,Line CN,,0,0,0,,她之所以行为异常
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.22,0:06:49.55,Line CN,,0,0,0,,是因为耳机从 Medical Mechanica 接收奇怪的电波
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.99,Line CN,,0,0,0,,奇怪的电波！
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.06,Line CN,,0,0,0,,要让她恢复正常
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.06,0:06:55.83,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我们必须同时摧毁接收器和发射源
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.83,0:06:58.23,Line CN,,0,0,0,,计划是这样的 我们分成两组行动
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.25,0:07:01.20,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这样我们可以分别攻击工厂的内侧和外侧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.49,0:07:04.14,Line CN,,0,0,0,,拉哈路 你负责摧毁外部天线
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.90,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.90,0:07:09.29,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我要和酷美一起潜入 摧毁设施的内部
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.28,Line CN,,0,0,0,,最后解开耳机
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.51,Line CN,,0,0,0,,喂 那是我的工作才对
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.88,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我绝不允许你和酷美待在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.88,0:07:17.18,Line CN,,0,0,0,,什什什么 等一下！
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.20,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我呢？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.40,0:07:22.45,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云—雀—弄！
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.47,0:07:24.52,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我是酷美！我在这！
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.04,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那么开始吧
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.62,0:07:54.52,Line CN,,0,0,0,,啊啊啊！不不不不！
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.19,0:08:01.16,Line CN,,0,0,0,,真是个好小伙子
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.47,0:08:08.37,Line CN,,0,0,0,,该进去了 -但是怎么进去？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.39,0:08:09.63,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你告诉我
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.74,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你连个计划都没有就好意思使唤我们？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.76,0:08:18.44,Line CN,,0,0,0,,不管你愿不愿意 我们只能一起想办法
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.48,0:08:19.44,Line CN,,0,0,0,,现在 合作一点！
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.44,0:08:21.51,Line CN,,0,0,0,,闭嘴！少来指挥我！
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.25,Line CN,,0,0,0,,真是没救了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.39,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这个宝物是个什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.39,0:08:29.35,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那个是森的女朋友的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.35,0:08:30.49,Line CN,,0,0,0,,还是别动它
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.49,0:08:32.41,Line CN,,0,0,0,,她花了很高的价钱买的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.41,0:08:33.53,Line CN,,0,0,0,,很高？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.83,Line CN,,0,0,0,,很高！
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.36,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你干什么呢？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.51,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你怎么就不明白？！
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.51,0:08:52.78,Line CN,,0,0,0,,它…它不想要你！
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.92,0:08:58.67,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你做了什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.65,0:09:01.69,Line CN,,0,0,0,,井出你这个蠢货 因为你尽干蠢事—
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.43,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我们必须这么做 因为这是证据
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.43,0:09:15.32,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但是我也感到内疚
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.30,0:09:16.29,Line CN,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.29,0:09:17.80,Line CN,,0,0,0,,因为有这个家伙
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.80,0:09:20.56,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我们的研究才能有这么大的进展
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.81,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这么说更准确 是因为这个家伙留下的空壳
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.68,Line CN,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.68,0:09:28.27,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这个空壳的主人不是一个生物
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.22,Line CN,,0,0,0,,至少在我们的语义中 不算是生物
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.35,0:09:34.45,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好像是在生物和星球之间的某种巨大存在
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.45,0:09:36.09,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那个星球可够大的
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.09,0:09:39.26,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么它的周期有数年之久
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.23,0:09:44.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.65,Line CN,,0,0,0,,是花盆！
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.63,0:09:49.32,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你搞丢的那个花盆吗？-它动了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.32,0:09:51.74,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那个东西只有对 N.O. 才会有反应
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.77,0:09:54.27,Line CN,,0,0,0,,说明 N.O. 通道打开了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.27,0:09:56.23,Line CN,,0,0,0,,他们居然得到了花盆
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.23,0:09:58.28,Line CN,,0,0,0,,而且流动逆转了！
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.85,0:10:00.91,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.98,0:10:05.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,他们被吸进你的脑袋里了 {日语拟声词求助}
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.18,0:10:10.26,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄 你到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.26,0:10:12.78,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你会永远这个样子吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.78,0:10:16.76,Line CN,,0,0,0,,嗯？你什么意思？我一直是这样
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.23,0:10:18.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,哈？一直？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.60,Line CN,,0,0,0,,实话说…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,从我记事起就是这样
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.00,0:10:30.61,Line CN,,0,0,0,,等等等等等等等等！啊—！
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.92,0:10:46.29,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你能不能闭嘴？啰嗦死了！
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.63,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你为什么不明白？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.65,0:10:50.90,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这不是他想要的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.90,0:10:53.80,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好像你很懂他一样 真是好笑
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.53,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我懂他
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.55,0:10:58.24,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你再说一遍 我就杀了你
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.66,Line CN,,0,0,0,,他需要自由
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.64,0:11:03.80,Line CN,,0,0,0,,任何想要拘束他的人都是我的敌人
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.81,0:11:05.46,Line CN,,0,0,0,,不管是 Medical Mechanica…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.48,0:11:07.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,还是你
Dialogue: 1,0:11:07.71,0:11:08.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,他…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.70,0:11:10.32,Line CN,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.35,0:11:12.54,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我受够了你谈论他
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.55,0:11:14.74,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我想要什么 就会去得到它
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.72,0:11:17.66,Line CN,,0,0,0,,只要能让他看见我 我会做任何事情
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.79,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你不会成功的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.81,0:11:24.00,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我全都理解
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.95,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我理解他
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.97,Line CN,,0,0,0,,也理解你
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.97,0:11:29.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你真敢说啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.70,0:11:31.76,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我会一直说
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.76,0:11:34.44,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你必须与我同心{希望有更模糊的译法：join 可以是合作/加入，也可以是指合为一体。虽然个人觉得仁由的意思是前者，而晴子故意理解为后者}{ts: 同心}
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.47,0:11:35.77,Line CN,,0,0,0,,毕竟 你就是我
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.84,0:11:39.64,Line CN,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.64,0:11:40.68,Line CN,,0,0,0,,拉哈路
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.68,0:11:42.53,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你终于明白了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.53,0:11:43.65,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我们一起的话 一定可以…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.67,0:11:45.55,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我要吞噬你
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.09,0:11:54.65,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.65,0:11:56.03,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你在哪 云雀弄？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.10,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄！
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.94,0:12:08.56,Line CN,,0,0,0,,小心！云雀弄！
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.56,0:12:11.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,视野真好！
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.17,0:12:16.41,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我的父亲在哪里{听力求助}{ts: どこですか}
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.43,0:12:17.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,啊 我把这个给忘了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.94,0:12:19.58,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你没有父亲的
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.39,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我也没有母亲
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.41,0:12:22.45,Line CN,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.47,0:12:25.12,Line CN,,0,0,0,,妈妈已经等了很久了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.14,0:12:27.63,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但是他还是不回家！
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.63,0:12:28.85,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄…
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.86,0:12:32.88,Line CN,,0,0,0,,如果一切都被毁掉 我们就能重新开始
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.88,0:12:35.93,Line CN,,0,0,0,,至少妈妈不会再伤心
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.95,0:12:39.50,Line CN,,0,0,0,,而且爸爸会和我们在一起
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.52,0:12:44.91,Line CN,,0,0,0,,如果今天和昨天一样 是平凡的一天 那样该有多好！
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.58,0:12:46.38,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄！
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.13,Line CN,,0,0,0,,天啊 差一点
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.16,0:13:03.55,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我不需要什么特别的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.55,0:13:07.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但是愤怒 悲伤 啜泣和哭喊
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.70,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我不想再听到了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.49,Line CN,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.20,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么这副耳机正适合我
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.64,0:13:21.01,Line CN,,0,0,0,,住手！拉哈路！
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.99,0:13:34.66,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄 我—
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.66,0:13:37.76,Line CN,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.78,0:13:43.47,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄！云雀弄！
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.08,0:13:52.14,Line CN,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.03,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄！
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.05,0:13:57.50,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你怎么了？！
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.50,0:13:58.65,Line CN,,0,0,0,,喂 回答我！
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.19,0:14:09.01,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那副耳机
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.83,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.15,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你恢复正常了？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.15,0:14:15.10,Line CN,,0,0,0,,井出
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.13,0:14:16.82,Line CN,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.82,0:14:20.11,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我 我要溢出来了{虽然说英文是overflow，但这不是术语，只是Mamimi自创的表达，表示自己情绪要失控，溢れちゃう，感觉还是有个"来"更接近？如果说“我要溢出了”，显得太术语太硬邦邦了。}{ts: OK}
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.13,0:14:22.77,Line CN,,0,0,0,,哈？-我要溢出来了！
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.79,0:14:26.54,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我要…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.18,Line CN,,0,0,0,,等等 那是什么意思？
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.67,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我 我要溢出来了！-云雀弄！
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我要溢出来了！
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.81,Line CN,,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.82,0:14:43.56,Line CN,,0,0,0,,世界… 要翻个底朝天了！{求助，词穷}
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.73,0:15:18.75,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.76,0:15:19.96,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那是什么？！
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.34,0:15:26.91,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄！
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.73,Line CN,,0,0,0,,天啊 难以置信
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.74,0:15:34.13,Line CN,,0,0,0,,-难道是海盗王？-不是！
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.37,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但那力量确实是他的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:35.38,0:15:37.62,Line CN,,0,0,0,,开始了！
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.32,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄！
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.90,Line CN,,0,0,0,,现在又是什么鬼！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.98,0:16:11.72,Line CN,,0,0,0,,下面发生了什么？！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.19,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这声音 什么在滚动？
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.72,0:16:18.99,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.83,0:16:24.56,Line CN,,0,0,0,,停手！拉哈路！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.60,0:16:25.32,Line CN,,0,0,0,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.33,0:16:28.20,Line CN,,0,0,0,,还有你的墨镜很逊！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.24,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你怎么敢？！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.78,0:16:42.05,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.18,0:16:46.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.12,0:16:48.65,Line CN,,0,0,0,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.05,0:16:51.49,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.23,0:16:56.43,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄！太好了 你醒了！
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.00,0:16:59.43,Line CN,,0,0,0,,井出？！
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.17,0:17:08.01,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄！我来了！
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.78,0:17:18.88,Line CN,,0,0,0,,放手吧 拉哈路！
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.15,0:17:22.95,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄！
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.97,0:17:24.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,井出！不！
Dialogue: 1,0:17:24.96,0:17:26.29,Line CN,,0,0,0,,啊 再加把劲
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.23,0:17:37.94,Line CN,,0,0,0,,天啊！对不起 我不是有意的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.97,0:17:39.46,Line CN,,0,0,0,,但是没时间说—啊啊！
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.34,Line CN,,0,0,0,,酷美！
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.44,0:17:47.41,Line CN,,0,0,0,,仁由！
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.75,0:17:52.92,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你最好不要放松警惕！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.49,0:18:02.26,Line CN,,0,0,0,,住手 拉哈路！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.28,0:18:06.73,Line CN,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 逊墨镜！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.75,0:18:08.37,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你没事吧？！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.39,0:18:10.07,Line CN,,0,0,0,,够了！拉哈路！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.63,Line CN,,0,0,0,,仁由！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.10,Line CN,,0,0,0,,仁由？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.09,0:18:43.23,Line CN,,0,0,0,,那那那个东西 要倒下来了！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.23,0:18:45.10,Line CN,,0,0,0,,喂 仁由？！
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.84,Line CN,,0,0,0,,别！住手！
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.91,0:19:24.08,Line CN,,0,0,0,,工厂…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.11,0:19:26.91,Line CN,,0,0,0,,竖起来了？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.62,0:19:39.99,Line CN,,0,0,0,,仁由
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.36,0:19:46.15,Line CN,,0,0,0,,拉—拉哈路…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.16,0:19:51.94,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我只是想让他获得自由
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.61,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我爱他
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.14,0:19:56.81,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这就是我的理由
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.24,0:20:00.87,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我想让他不受我们的拘束
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.91,0:20:03.11,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你不明白喵
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.55,0:20:08.14,Line CN,,0,0,0,,一切都是属于他的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.14,0:20:10.52,Line CN,,0,0,0,,从一开始就是如此
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.56,0:20:13.64,Line CN,,0,0,0,,他的镣铐和他的自由
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.66,0:20:17.28,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这个世界里没有什么是不属于他的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.30,0:20:19.48,Line CN,,0,0,0,,没有例外
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.50,0:20:22.42,Line CN,,0,0,0,,这就解决了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.47,Line CN,,0,0,0,,所以我们到头来还是不一样
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.64,0:20:29.33,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我也这么想
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.34,0:20:32.43,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你也许是对的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.44,0:20:34.60,Line CN,,0,0,0,,到我这里来吧 仁由
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.60,0:20:37.45,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我们终于可以到一起了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.49,0:21:17.68,Line CN,,0,0,0,,你也跟我来吧？怎么样？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.68,0:21:20.12,Line CN,,0,0,0,,酷美？
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.63,Line CN,,0,0,0,,云雀弄！
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.03,0:21:31.27,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.27,0:21:33.62,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.62,0:21:36.14,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我知道你想要做什么了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.41,0:21:40.04,Line CN,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.52,Line CN,,0,0,0,,我不能跟你走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:15.13,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me -- I didn't see nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:18.73,Line EN,,0,0,0,,'cause Ide was the one who went off on his own and did whatever it is he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:27.67,Line EN,,0,0,0,,When she came back from the beach, I was worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:29.68,Line EN,,0,0,0,,because she was unconscious for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:32.71,Line EN,,0,0,0,,But as soon as she woke up, she was suddenly all perky and happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.71,0:00:34.88,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I think it's because she could sense my love for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:38.10,Line EN,,0,0,0,,And now, for the first time ever, I actually feel like her mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:40.02,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Whoa! There's a chopper, a chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:42.32,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The world is turning upside down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.32,0:00:44.86,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'm so pissed off I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.86,0:00:47.19,Line EN,,0,0,0,,And it's all 'cause of those piece-of-shit headphones!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:50.73,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's an emergency measure put in place by Medical Mechanica.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:53.28,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The change in personality is mostly likely a side effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.63,0:00:54.95,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh! The Iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:57.77,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Also known as the World Smoother!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.44,0:01:01.04,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Well, to be honest, I do think she's pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:07.91,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.95,0:01:09.32,Line EN,,0,0,0,,it's not Hibajiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.06,0:01:13.29,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Mm, top of the morning, fellow classmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:15.89,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hidomi is here, bright and early!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:18.56,Line EN,,0,0,0,,She's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:40.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Ms. Haruko, do something, I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:43.88,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's your fault. You didn't take off those headphones like I asked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:45.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,And I'm really sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:48.49,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You're wasting precious time that we don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:51.12,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You know what you need to do, so do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:54.79,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-Do you enjoy dressing up like a maid? -Medical Mechanica.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:57.60,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's where we can remove them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.86,0:02:00.93,Line EN,,0,0,0,,And then you and I can chase after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:04.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,We don't have any other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:10.38,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hope I'm not late for work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:16.78,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Ugh. That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:19.25,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:21.02,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:22.55,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's all done!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.29,0:02:29.35,Line EN,,0,0,0,,In a single word, this is a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:32.16,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-A song? -That's right-o!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:35.50,Line EN,,0,0,0,,There's no oxygen in space, so no one can hear you sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:40.71,Line EN,,0,0,0,,But the stars spin and spin and they spin around and around and they sing together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:48.01,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The music of the stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:49.82,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:58.76,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, cool! They're putting in a new ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:02:59.96,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:08.50,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Your time is up. You need to pay me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:11.37,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:16.11,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Nice doing business. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:19.51,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-Did I just buy this? -Precisely. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.11,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Till the next time you need my services.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:28.05,Line EN,,0,0,0,,-What is that? -It's just a Viking ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:30.19,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's lame. Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:31.88,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:34.73,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm just glad you made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:36.55,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What's that, Mr. Tonkichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:38.22,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hmm? This?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:41.23,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's about to be our new main attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:44.82,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You can't find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:47.37,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Well, stop acting like a child and look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:51.36,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I already looked everywhere for it, but it's nowhere to be found!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:55.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Who in the hell loses something as big as a flower pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:56.82,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Can't you just make another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:04:00.05,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's a one-of-a-kind thing made from this guy's parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:04.36,Line EN,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can make another one from scratch, not with our technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:10.23,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, have you seen a carved bear that used to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:14.12,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You're such a... That's not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:15.80,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'm home, homeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:18.87,Line EN,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to use it to monitor -Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:21.57,Line EN,,0,0,0,,We want to reverse the current of the N.O.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:25.88,Line EN,,0,0,0,,If we hypothesize that N.O. is a power that can pull objects from elsewhere, then --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.88,0:04:30.68,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I see. Then it stands to reason we should be able to reverse the direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.58,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's right. And... Mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.29,0:04:45.63,Line EN,,0,0,0,,1, 2, punch it! Now, reverse the flow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:51.47,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, Aiko. Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:54.97,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh! Look at that! You've got what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:58.44,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Those are amazing fists you have! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:01.21,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You let the champion guy inside the house again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:02.05,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:04.58,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You and I could take over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:09.44,Line EN,,0,0,0,,This girl packs a punch like a shooting star!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:15.43,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The neighbors are already whispering about why a weird homeless dude is always visiting our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.32,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry. -Your dad has done no wrong, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:20.90,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Your dad's a champ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:23.20,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'll give you these, if you forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:27.21,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You're always pushing these comp tickets on me as reparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.04,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Where the hell are you getting them from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:31.11,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.97,Line EN,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:36.15,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'd rather have a day pass to the spa or some resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.17,0:05:38.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I know the amusement park got a brand-new ride,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.12,Line EN,,0,0,0,,but it turns out, it's just a lame Viking ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.36,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It was installed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:47.58,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It was the Viking ship?! You're sure?! -Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:50.33,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hey. They did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:51.46,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.67,Line EN,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be a real issue for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:57.36,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? -Oh, hey, Aiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.36,0:05:59.67,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Do you know where the carved bear is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.97,0:06:06.11,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate you being the guinea pig for our test run.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:08.18,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's part of the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:11.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I just love what a good sport you always are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:13.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Besides, I get bonus pay for this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.92,0:06:16.34,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's right. You need the money? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:17.99,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.61,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I-I wanted to buy a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:23.80,Line EN,,0,0,0,,A dream. A dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.83,0:06:26.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What is the reason we dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.23,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Could it be because it is called a dream?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:30.60,Line EN,,0,0,0,,There are dreams while we sleep and dreams while we're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:32.50,Line EN,,0,0,0,,We dream whether we're sleeping or awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:34.64,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I have a dream! I dreamed that I woke up in a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:35.51,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.14,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.65,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Those headphones are going to be impossible to remove.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:44.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,They're too deep inside Hidomi's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:46.22,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The reason why she's acting this way is because
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:49.55,Line EN,,0,0,0,,the headphones are receiving bizarre radiowaves from Medical Mechanica.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:50.99,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Bizarre radiowaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.06,Line EN,,0,0,0,,To get her back to normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:55.83,Line EN,,0,0,0,,we need to simultaneously destroy the receptor and the transmission source.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.83,0:06:58.23,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Here's the plan -- We'll split into two groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:01.20,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That way, we can attack the Plant from the inside and outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.49,0:07:04.14,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Raharu, you will destroy the outer antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.90,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:09.29,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I will sneak in with Hidomi, destroy the facility inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.28,Line EN,,0,0,0,,and lastly, unlock the headphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.51,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hey! But that should be my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:15.88,Line EN,,0,0,0,,There's no way I am leaving Hidomi alone with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.88,0:07:17.18,Line EN,,0,0,0,,W-W-What, what? Uh, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.20,Line EN,,0,0,0,,W-What about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:22.45,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hi--ba--ji--ri--!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:24.52,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's me! Hidomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.04,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:54.52,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Aaaaaah! No, no, no, no, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:01.16,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What a good sport he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:08.37,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Time to go in.  -But from where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:09.63,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.74,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You don't have a plan and you're bossing us around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:18.44,Line EN,,0,0,0,,We have to figure this out together, whether you like it or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:19.44,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Now, be useful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:21.51,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I don't take orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.25,Line EN,,0,0,0,,We're getting nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.39,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What is this treasure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:29.35,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Oh. That's Mori's girlfriend's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:30.49,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Best not touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:32.41,Line EN,,0,0,0,,She paid a really high price for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:33.53,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Really high?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.83,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Really high!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.83,0:08:36.36,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.51,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Why can't you just get it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:52.78,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It doesn't... It doesn't want you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:58.67,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:01.69,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Ide! You're an idiot, 'cause you do idiotic thin....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.43,Line EN,,0,0,0,,We have to do this, because it's evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:15.32,Line EN,,0,0,0,,But I do feel a bit bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:16.29,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:17.80,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Because of this guy here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:20.56,Line EN,,0,0,0,,our research made a lot of progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.81,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Or rather because of the shell that's left of him, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.68,Line EN,,0,0,0,,So true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:28.27,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The owner of the shell isn't a living creature,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.22,Line EN,,0,0,0,,at least, not in our sense of the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:34.45,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's almost like a larger being that's between a living creature and a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:36.09,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The planet's quite big.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:39.26,Line EN,,0,0,0,,And that's why its cycle lasts years at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:44.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.65,Line EN,,0,0,0,,It's the flower pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:49.32,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You mean, the one that you lost? -It's moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:51.74,Line EN,,0,0,0,,And that thing only activates in reaction to N.O.!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:54.27,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That means the N.O. must be open.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:56.23,Line EN,,0,0,0,,They've actually got ahold of the flower pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:58.28,Line EN,,0,0,0,,And it's in reverse flow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:00.91,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:05.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,They went inside your head! Bicu-bicu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:10.26,Line EN,,0,0,0,, Hibajiri... What exactly happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:12.78,Line EN,,0,0,0,,And are you gonna stay this hyper forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:16.76,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hmm? What do you mean? I've always been like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:18.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Huh? Always?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.60,Line EN,,0,0,0,,To be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,as long as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:30.61,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait! Wait, wait, wait, wait! Wait! Aaaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:46.29,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Will you shut up? You're such a broken record!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.63,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Why can't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:50.90,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That is not what he wants, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:53.80,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Funny how you seem to think you know him so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.53,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Well, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:58.24,Line EN,,0,0,0,,If you say that again, I'm gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.66,Line EN,,0,0,0,,He needs to have his freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:03.80,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Anyone who tries to keep him tied down is my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:05.46,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Medical Mechanica...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:07.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,and even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:08.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,He just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:10.32,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:12.54,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of hearing you talk about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:14.74,Line EN,,0,0,0,,When I want something, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:17.66,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'll do what I need to make sure he sees me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.79,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You're going to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:24.00,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I understand everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.95,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I understand him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.97,Line EN,,0,0,0,,And you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:29.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,How dare you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:31.76,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I will keep on saying it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:34.44,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You need to join me, Raharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:35.77,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You're me, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:39.64,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:40.68,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Raharu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:42.53,Line EN,,0,0,0,,you finally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:43.65,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Together, I know we can --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.67,0:11:45.55,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I am gonna devour you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:54.65,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:56.03,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Hibajiri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.10,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:08.56,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri! W-Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:11.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I can see everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:16.41,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Where is, どこですか, my father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:17.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I forgot about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:19.58,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You don't have a father, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.39,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I don't have a mother, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:22.45,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:25.12,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Mommy's been waiting a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:27.63,Line EN,,0,0,0,,but he still won't come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:28.85,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:32.88,Line EN,,0,0,0,,If everything's destroyed, then we can start over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:35.93,Line EN,,0,0,0,,For one, Mom would no longer be crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:39.50,Line EN,,0,0,0,,And also, Dad would still be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:44.91,Line EN,,0,0,0,,If today was an ordinary day, like yesterday, that would've been, oh, so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:46.38,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.13,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, man, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:03.55,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I don't need anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:07.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,But the anger, the sadness, the sobbing and crying,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.70,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.49,Line EN,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.20,Line EN,,0,0,0,,that's why these are perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:21.01,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Raharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:34.66,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri, I --
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:37.76,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:43.47,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri? Hibajiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.08,0:13:52.14,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.03,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:57.50,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:58.65,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hey, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:09.01,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The headphones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.83,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hibajiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.15,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Are you back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:15.10,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:16.82,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Whoa. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:20.11,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I-I think I'm going to overflow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:22.77,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm going to overflow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:26.54,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.18,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Wait. What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.67,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'm going to overflow! -Hibajiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I'm going to overflow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.81,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:43.56,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The world... is turning inside out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:18.75,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:19.96,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.34,0:15:26.91,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:32.73,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Whoa. I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:34.13,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Is that the Pirate Ki--? -It's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:35.37,Line EN,,0,0,0,,But that power is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:37.62,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Uh, it's begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.32,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hibajiri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:54.90,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:11.72,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What is happening down there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.19,Line EN,,0,0,0,,What's that rolling sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:18.99,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:24.56,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Cut it out! Raharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:25.32,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:28.20,Line EN,,0,0,0,,And your sunglasses are lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:39.24,Line EN,,0,0,0,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:42.05,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:46.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:48.65,Line EN,,0,0,0,,てめぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.05,0:16:51.49,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:56.43,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri?! Good, you woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:16:59.43,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Ide?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:08.01,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri! I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:18.88,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Give up, Raharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:22.95,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:24.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Ide, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:26.29,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:37.94,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Oh, God! Uh, sorry, I didn't mean to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:39.46,Line EN,,0,0,0,,But we don't have time to discu-- Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:40.34,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hidomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:47.41,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Jinyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:52.92,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You'd better not let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:02.26,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Raharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:06.73,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Lame Glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:08.37,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:10.07,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's enough! Raharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.63,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Jinyu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.10,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Uh, Jinyu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.09,0:18:43.23,Line EN,,0,0,0,,T-T-That thing over there is falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:45.10,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jinyu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:49.84,Line EN,,0,0,0,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:24.08,Line EN,,0,0,0,,The Plant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:26.91,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Stood up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:39.99,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Jinyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:46.15,Line EN,,0,0,0,,R-Raharu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:51.94,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I just wanted for him to have his freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.61,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.14,0:19:56.81,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:20:00.87,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I want him to be free from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.91,0:20:03.11,Line EN,,0,0,0,,You don't get it, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:08.14,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Everything has always belonged to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:10.52,Line EN,,0,0,0,,right from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:13.64,Line EN,,0,0,0,,His shackles and his freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.66,0:20:17.28,Line EN,,0,0,0,,There isn't anything in this world that doesn't belong to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.30,0:20:19.48,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:22.42,Line EN,,0,0,0,,That settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.47,Line EN,,0,0,0,,So we're not the same, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:29.33,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:32.43,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:34.60,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Come with me, Jinyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:37.45,Line EN,,0,0,0,,We can finally be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:17.68,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Now, why don't you come with me, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:20.12,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hidomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:21.63,Line EN,,0,0,0,,Hibajiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:31.27,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:33.62,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I finally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:36.14,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I know what you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.41,0:21:40.04,Line EN,,0,0,0,,And that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:44.52,Line EN,,0,0,0,,I can't go with you.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.13,0:04:16.14,Line CN - Top,,0,0,0,,重要的是那个花盆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:16.16,Line EN - Top,,0,0,0,,The important thing is the flower pot.
